<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3363400>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A–C. Arctozenus risso (Bonaparte, 1840).A. Original drawing which Paralepis risso Bonaparte, 1840, reproduced from Cuvier in Cuvier & Valenciennes, 1829: pl. fig. 66). B. Neotype of Paralepis risso Bonaparte, 1840, MNHN 2018-0246. C. MNHN uncat. (tissue no. BPS-1960), 199 mm SL, photo by Samuel Iglésias. D–E. Arctozenus australis sp. nov. D. Holotype, MNHN 2000-0260. E. Fresh condition, one of paratypes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3363400/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

